GiantTN

The undirected graph GiantTN has 25689 nodes and 38904929 edges.

RAM requirements

The RAM requirements for the nodes and edges data structures are 3.46MB and 53.49MB respectively.

Degree centrality

The nodes with highest degree centrality are: 11026 (degree 4266 and weighted degree 4266), 22990 (degree 4641 and weighted degree 4641), 51523 (degree 5130 and weighted degree 5130), 26003 (degree 4734 and weighted degree 4734) and 23509 (degree 4902 and weighted degree 4902).
